HEATMAP with Testis/Tumor-Specific genes per cancer type

data_completed_TSA_forced = data_completed_TSA %>% select(-TPM)
data_completed_TSA_wide = data_completed_TSA_forced %>% subset(forced_TPM > 0)
## select only the patients for which the gene is TSA
## we compute the median of the patients that express the gene in a tumor-specific manner
data_completed_TSA_wide = data_completed_TSA_wide %>% group_by(gene_name,ctype) %>% mutate(medianTPM = median(forced_TPM)) %>% ungroup()
